    "summary": "Finance generalist with extensive experience in pensions management. Has had an international career with Shell and worked in pensions and investment related functions  in different roles i.e. as Controller, Head of pension administration and actuarial matters and as internal actuary. He holds a Master's degree in Economics from the University of Amsterdam and studied actuarial science. Other positions held during his career with Shell are internal auditor at Pernis Refinery, Head of Audit in Brunei, Head of Finance Operations in Gabon, Head of economics Group Materials and Business Finance Manager in Nigeria. Head global Standardisation, Outsourcing, Custody and Trustee support at Shell Treasury, Group Pensions. Director of Stichting Barbizon, the Depositary of SAMCo Asset pools. Director Pension Fund Board.",
